{"type": "article", "id": 53217, "title": "一张小办公桌，设计几乎没有任何冗余｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-05-15T23:09:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47706, "name": "Northern"}, {"id": 48806, "name": "Yonoh"}, {"id": 19566, "name": "Note Design Studio"}, {"id": 23565, "name": "Fogia"}, {"id": 11017, "name": "建筑营"}, {"id": 39676, "name": "Sancal"}, {"id": 50274, "name": "Ab Rogers Design"}, {"id": 23351, "name": "Tom Fereday"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 184, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180516070928tlZsoHv07JjyLhrc.JPG", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Bespoke Furniture for Students by Ab Rogers Design</h3><p>伦敦工作室 Ab Rogers Design 设计了一系列适合学生用的家具，是为豪华学生公寓开发商 Scape 量身而做。整个系列包括一把椅子和一个凳子，没有复杂的机械零件，但却功能多样化。</p><p>比如这把四面卷曲的橙色凳子，每一面都可以承担不同的功能，适用于包括学习、放松、吃饭多种场景，还可以用来挂外套。蓝色的椅子还附带了边桌功能，随手放杯咖啡或者茶，甚至笔记本电脑，都很方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221440EDM72TaWwelJuFLP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805152214427TsEWbgqCZ8lV0mh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221447HQZdB258KxUXTOkw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221452oijFxYBSImhz1lGV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.422166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221456XadfZWVJG04bCrc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.396785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>COSAS Collection by Sancal</h3><p>西班牙家具品牌 Sancal 在 2018 年米兰设计周上推出 COSAS 系列，再一次表达了其结合了幽默感和艺术性的设计风格。整个系列包括艺术装饰风格的毯子、靠垫以及部分时尚配饰。</p><p>名为 Born Free 的毯子给人一种诙谐的感觉，出自立陶宛艺术家 Egle Zvirblyte 之手，温暖的色彩搭配柔软轻薄的材料，和阴郁的冬天或是慵懒的假期都很搭。另有几条毛毯，也都是色彩明亮的风格，灵感出自艺术家的插图作品。</p><p>Flower Power 花瓶同样是图形元素的艺术化再创作。坐垫和抱枕也都是一些有趣的彩色插画图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k0654p3qev8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221538GHyu8lPa4mZkM9TA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221539qRjEu0DtFyTnYNv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221544jnJG10gLYkyQcoZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221544x6KkJvXZ7cUIefCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759234\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221552IwUGnP2Cvb1NV9Ms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756793\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221557q8ic4QLhMfYNzBrI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221602rsOKdmULk2jXnBIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680764\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221603MGb1JqEpUZyRCPTX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754768\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>框镜 by 建筑营</h3><p>这是建筑营设计工作室的设计师李晓明的新作框镜。人与空间的游戏关系在这个作品中成为关键。空间借由立方体与六个面的关系建立起来，同样借助于二维框镜与三维空间的视错转换，框镜时而平面时而立体。</p><p>框镜有三部分结构构成，三个独立的结构可以自由组合、拼接，空间可以由二维转换为三维，由三个部分组合的形式决定，使用者可以根据使用空间的性质与氛围随时切换框镜的形式构成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><br></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221632EDUqCcd0uP9yk3KS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.068500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221739FOu7zJ9vxoaCVHmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.530000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805152217404jg8Qew0knVNJ5iX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.957333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221740XyDro7pM9qI1U8R4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.147143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221632nFQTItiAfH2VmyKd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.514500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221632u4SwThH7a1UCiFAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.957500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MITO LIGHT by Tom Fereday</h3><p>为了展示天然材料的自然美特性，澳大利亚设计师 Tom Fereday 设计了 MITO 照明系列，结合了精密的制造技术和天然木材、石头，创造出一种被精雕细琢出来的照明氛围。</p><p>温暖的间接光源从天然材料制成的穹顶结构中微微溢出，模块化的设计亦允许 MITO 系列转到不同角度，创造层次分明的照明效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221812MalyKPpn7YASCD9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221812OEt3aAb4TgGInPqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221812FkxqAKVvw7zEt06T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221812OVr2usTmSZfcEMi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221812mfntO1pR8cLAsekH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805152218137fWkMXr0q6gZD9bQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.tomfereday.com/lighting/mito/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tom Fereday</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Archetto by Note Design Studio for Fogia</h3><p>瑞典家具品牌 Fogia 和斯德哥尔摩设计工作室 Note Design Studio 合作频密，从椅子、沙发到收纳柜都能看到双方的合作成果。</p><p>这款名为 Archetto 的壁挂式搁架，是其 Arch 系列的一款产品，拱形条状的底部搭配圆形托盘的结构看起来很精巧，它可以单独使用，也可以组合使用，排布在墙壁上，布置合理的话，也可以是创意十足的墙面装饰物，美观程度取决于你会在托盘上放些什么。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018051522191905MRkmiN4XFcpUKy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221919WpLfc8KoMdnNjgDS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333065\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221920dWlPBiOekTGDw1p5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515221918RVQi7M1g2B6yhdSc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332957\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://notedesignstudio.se/archetto/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Note Design Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Shelter by Yonoh for Northern</h3><p>奥斯陆新品牌 Northern 推出办公桌 Shelter，正如其名，设计师希望为工作学习状态中的人们提供一个“安全的避风港”。</p><p>这款办公桌出自西班牙家居设计工作室 Yonoh 之手，设计几乎没有冗余功能，熏制橡木桌面搭配穿孔钢制围挡，将用户的注意力和情绪集中在桌面上。此外，桌面上还设有线缆穿插的孔，包括耳机、夹子等物件也可以收纳在围挡上，随手拿用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515222023kYB8fDFOwsg5AV7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404803\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515222023lmBOZEJ3CINpiv6S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404803\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180515222023WOsZ5ry6Md3klqvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805152220240j41fyWZEH9IeQNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404803\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://northern.no/wr/product/shelter/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Northern</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}